  "description": "The gray two-chamber refrigerator has replenished the model range of the Toshiba brand in 2022 and represents solutions at the junction of the middle and advanced class. There are two cooling circuits and external touch control, which means that you can flexibly adjust the temperature conditions in each of the chambers without even opening the unit. The high level of overall reliability of the device is confirmed by the presence of an inverter compressor, and thanks to the Full No Frost system, unpleasant manual defrosting procedures will be a thing of the past. With a case size of 202x60x66 cm, the Toshiba GR-RB500WE-PMJ refrigerator boasts a volume of 360 liters, which can satisfy the needs of even large families. Below is a 104-liter freezer, the space of which is divided between three drawers. They can freeze up to 14 kg of food per day. And if there are blackouts, then the cold inside should last up to 15 hours. The 256-liter refrigerator compartment has freshness and humidity zones (suitable for meat (fish) and vegetables with fruits, respectively), three open shelves and a hanging bottle holder (for 5 pieces). Other features worth highlighting are A++ class energy consumption, a door close indicator and a child lock feature.",
